{"id":102,"count":2,"description":"Escape to the sun, sand, and sea with a refreshing short break in Goa, India\u2019s most loved beach destination. Unwind on the golden shores of Calangute, Baga, and Anjuna, or soak in the serenity of South Goa\u2019s quiet beaches like Palolem and Colva. Explore Portuguese-era churches in Old Goa, stroll through vibrant flea markets, and enjoy the buzzing nightlife that Goa is famous for. Adventure lovers can indulge in water sports like parasailing, jet skiing, and scuba diving, while food enthusiasts can savor authentic Goan seafood and beach shack vibes. Whether it\u2019s relaxation, culture, or fun-filled activities, Goa offers the perfect blend for a quick yet memorable getaway.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/short-break-goa\/","name":"SHORT BREAK GOA","slug":"short-break-goa","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/SHORT-BREAK-GOA.png","filesize":831495,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"SHORT-BREAK-GOA-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":72555,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/SHORT-BREAK-GOA-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"SHORT-BREAK-GOA-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":30856,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/SHORT-BREAK-GOA-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"SHORT-BREAK-GOA-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":375060,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/SHORT-BREAK-GOA-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"SHORT-BREAK-GOA-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":99901,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/SHORT-BREAK-GOA-374x226.png"},"destination-thumb-size":{"file":"SHORT-BREAK-GOA-600x596.png","